```

Compiler gives this error (line numbers won't match up because i simplified it for this post)
```
error[E0277]: the trait bound `rocket_contrib::Json<models::user::UserMessage>: rocket::request::FromRequest<'_, '_>` is not satisfied
  --> src/guards/auth.rs:44:39
   |
44 |                 let outcome = request.guard::<Json<UserMessage>>();
   |                                       ^^^^^ the trait `rocket::request::FromRequest<'_, '_>` is not implemented for `rocket_contrib::Json<models::user::UserMessage>`
```
